features: TRUE SPACE SAVING: BAGSMART 6 set compression packing cubes work just like a vacuum sealer. After the clothes are packed, use the compression zipper in the middle of the bag to help flatten the clothes and expel excess air, saving up to 60% of storage space. Say goodbye to bulky packing and make the most out of every inch!

LIGHTWEIGHT TRAVEL ESSENTIALS: Lightweight fabric ensures your clothes fit neatly into your luggage without adding extra weight. These travel packing cubes are perfect when you want to reduce weight and save space in your carry-on, suitcase or backpack.

PREMIUM QUALITY & DURABLE: Made from premium polyester and high-density mesh, these travel packing cubes can withstand daily wear and tear and are reusable, ensuring your belongings stay intact during your travels. The bag's zippers have been rigorously tested many times to ensure smooth operation and reduce the possibility of snagging, allowing you to open and close the packing organizers cube with ease.

MULTI-FUNCTIONAL & MULTIPURPOSE: Whether you carry airline carry-on luggage, duffle bags, backpacks or handbags, these suitacses organizers bag sets are sure to fit compactly without taking up a lot of space. You can take these travel cubes with you on business trips, camping adventures, and vacations to keep your clothes, toiletries, and other accessories separate, or you can use them at home as cupboard storage organizers to keep your wardrobe tidy.

PERFECT STORAGE ASSISTANT: These travel must have cubes includes 1 large cube (11.6'' x 15.9''), 2 medium cubes (9.2'' x 13''), 2 small cubes (8.2'' x 11.4'' '') and a drawstring shoe bag (13" x 17.7"). Packing cubes of different sizes are used for different packing purposes. You can separate clothes (such as jackets, pants, t-shirts and socks) into different packing cubes for easy access.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So far so good.
reviews.reviewText: We bought these for an upcoming trip, and we have not actually used them yet. My review is based on first impressions. The bags are attractive and appear to be well made. A close examination of all the bags (we ordered two identical sets) did not show any manufacturing flaws. The zippers all worked well and appeared to be well sewn in. That’s especially important for the compression zippers, because they are going to have to cope with a lot of stress. So, first impressions are very positive. Time will tell if they actually perform as well as they appear.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good set of packing cubes
reviews.reviewText: I love that all the bags fit within one bag to make storage when they’re not in use really easy. The color is amazing light green and beautiful. Big variety of sizes of items for each of the bags. There’s five compression bags plus a little shoe/laundry bag. My initial thoughts once I was opening the bags themselves is that they get pretty deep when fully unzipped which is exciting. As somebody who really loves packing cubes in terms of organization and compartmentalization for different clothing items when traveling my initial thoughts are that while there are a lot of packing cubes in this set 3 of them are all the same size and might not fit as much in them as a few larger cubes would. In the common, medium size cube, I was able to fit a sweatshirt, summer dress and a light raincoat in it and got the compression zipper to go all the way around. I didn’t have to push so much and a pull tab helped me to get it zipped. Overall the second zipper seems like it struggled a little bit but in the end got there. I tend to overpack and I like to think this system would let me pack all the things I’d like without compromising space in my suitcase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great product, wont compress 60%, pretty durable
reviews.reviewText: Item:BAGSMART Compression Packing Cubes for Travel, 6 Set Travel Packing Cubes for Suitcases, Compression Suitcases Organizers Bag Set for Travel Essentials, Lightweight Packing Organizers Black (Black)Pros:-Good for organization. Keeping things separated in bags helps you find things quicker.-Compresses ok (see cons. Also see pics). The compression mechanism works by a zipper. So that means it compresses the outside-Easy to use-Seems durable, I think it will last a long time, but not forever-Comes with 5 compressible bags and 1 extra bag/laundry type bagCons:-So their claim of 60% compression is a little far fetched. The only thing that gets compressed is the outside and not the inside really. The more stuff you put in the bag the less your compression ratio.Other Thoughts:-All these types of products are all claiming 60%, when in reality, none of them are going to reach 60%.
